  <h4>Create your own event</h4>
  <p>Bring people together, or turn your passion into a business.
    <br>
    EventX gives you everything you need to host your best event yet.</p>

  <%= link_to "Create Event", events_new_path, class: "btn-large z-depth-0",
              style: "background-color: #EED8AE; color: #000000"  %>

</div>
